msgid   "<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore "
        "the Manjaro boot\n"
        "installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
        "\n"
        "<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting "
        "correctly there are no problems in the boot, so it is\n"
        "better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
        "<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other "
        "Linux distributions.</span>\n"
        "\n"
        "Do you want to proceed?"
